    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>cornflour</strong> to a plate with the <strong>remaining ground smoked paprika </strong>and a very generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, and mix until fully combined</p><p>Pat your <strong>hake fillet[s]</strong> dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Place the <strong>hake fillet[s] </strong>onto the floured plate, pressing firmly to coat evenly on both sides – this is your <strong>coated hake</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1682084178076-x200.jpg",
