            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the fish is cooking, slice your<strong> brioche bun[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Once the fries are lightly golden, remove the tray[s] from the oven, push the fries to one side and add the <strong>brioche bun halves</strong> to the other side, cut-side down</p><p>Return the tray[s]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>to the oven for a final 4-5 min or until the brioche is warmed through and the fries are golden and crisp – these are your <strong>smoky fries</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
