            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>To build your burger, top a<strong> warmed brioche bun base</strong> with a <strong>Baja-style hake fillet</strong>, a drizzle of <strong>lime mayo</strong>, some of the <strong>chilli-lime slaw</strong> and a <strong>warmed brioche bun lid</strong> – this is your <strong>Baja-style hake burger</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>smoky fries</strong> and <strong>remaining chilli-lime slaw</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
